Generator pull request comments 
* mirror_to 
* customer-project 
* validator changes pipeline url 
* git flow pipeline url  


customer hidden project 
1. generator pipeline
    * mounts files from validator 
    * runs generator
    * create files 


customer view project 
1. validator pipeline 
    * Merge master if no conflicts on PR (rebase) 
    * Runs validator
    * copies files to generator pipeline
    * triggers generator pipeline

2. git flow pipeline
    * get current pr number and event type from github action
    * if merge
        - merge the pr 
        - get list of all open PRs
        - rebase latest changes from main to PR branch
        - push to PR branch, this will auto trigger validator pipeline
    * if close
        - close the PR 



Github action
1. After TG apply
    * read source pr number from description
    * read git flow pipeline url from description
    * trigger the git flow pipeline in source repo to merge the source PR by passing PR number as variable
    * get list of open pull requests for the same customer-project 
        - if source same as merged PR, ignore
        - if source different, trigger validator/generator pipeline
    
