what are the inputs required to run validator 
- customer 
    * CDA_EXECUTION_TYPE (possible values cutomer/ops)
    * CDA_CONFIGS
    * no need of prscope file 
- OPS
    * CDA_EXECUTION_TYPE (possible values cutomer/ops)
    * CDA_CONFIGS
    * GITHUB_TOKEN


what does validator produce
- just checks for errors 

What are the inputs to generator 
- customer 
    * CDA_CUSTOMER_CONFIGS - root repo contens
    * GITHUB_TOKEN 
    * CDA_BUFFER_REPO - github location of buffer repo (https/ssh)
    * CDA_BUFFER_REPO_BRANCH -  master(mostly master)
    * CDA_OUTPUT_LOCATION
- ops 
    * CDA_OPS_CONFIGS
    * GITHUB_TOKEN
    * CDA_BUFFER_REPO - github location of buffer repo (https/ssh)
    * CDA_BUFFER_REPO_BRANCH -  master(mostly master)
    * CDA_OUTPUT_LOCATION





what does generator produce 
- can clear volumes everytime before run


